    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Support the Constituent Assembly (CA) members to review gender responsive provisions for the new Constitution in line with international standards [CEDAW]\r\n\r\nSupport discussion and dissemination of the Constitution background note at the local level       \r\nSupport the Parliamentary Steering Committee on Women and Children in collaboration with MoWCSW/NWC to take forward the GE provisions  \r\n                            \r\nContinue advocacy through the UN interagency group on citizenship\r\n\r\nFacilitate interaction between  CA members and GE advocates (CSAG) on the gender responsive provisions of the new Constitution and its implementation \r\n\r\nSupport ECN Gender unit and participate in GESI committee meetings at ECN\r\n\r\nSupport roundtables with women’s group (CSAG)  to develop advocacy strategies to increase women’s representation across sectors"
      },
      "ne": null
